<PB REF="032877_0002_0FF5A7AB804778E0">
<P>AN HISTORICAL AND GEOGRAPHICAL ACCOUNT OF ALGIERS; COMPREHENDING A NOVEL AND INTERESTING <HI>DETAIL OF EVENTS</HI> RELATIVE TO THE AMERICAN CAPTIVES.</P>
<P>BY JAMES WILSON STEVENS.</P>
<P><HI>PHILADELPHIA:</HI> PRINTED BY <HI>HOGAN &amp; M'ELROY,</HI> GEORGE-STREET THIRD DOOR BELOW SOUTH-STREET.</P>
<P>Augu&s;t, 1797.</P>
</DIV1>
