<CELL>111,033</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>The pre&s;ent price is 86, with little de|mand; &s;uppo&s;e the remaining 249 m. dollars produce 3<HI>&s;</HI>9 per dollar, the amount will be</CELL>
